      <title>瑞士检察官放弃对银行博客的调查</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/swiss-prosecutors-drop-probe-into-banking-blog-2025-12-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏黎世检察官结束了对瑞士一家领先银行博客的调查，该博客的办公室今年夏天因涉嫌违反银行保密法而遭到突击搜查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/swiss-prosecutors-drop-probe-into-banking-blog-2025-12-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Dec 2025 17:10:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国 Secure Trust 将以 6.19 亿美元出售汽车金融业务</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uks-secure-trust-sell-motor-finance-business-619-million-2025-12-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国安全信托银行周三表示，将以 4.586 亿英镑（6.1948 亿美元）的价格将其消费汽车金融业务出售给欧洲投资基金管理公司 LCM Partners 管理的基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uks-secure-trust-sell-motor-finance-business-619-million-2025-12-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Dec 2025 12:40:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国石油公司 (BP) 将嘉实多 65% 的股份以 60 亿美元出售给 Stonepeak</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/bp-nears-deal-sell-majority-stake-castrol-stonepeak-wsj-reports-2025-12-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该协议是该石油公司迄今为止最雄心勃勃的资产出售，因为该公司试图削减债务并提高回报，同时缩减可再生能源投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/bp-nears-deal-sell-majority-stake-castrol-stonepeak-wsj-reports-2025-12-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Dec 2025 03:16:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Blackstone 的 LivCor 就司法部的租金定价索赔达成和解</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-proposes-resolve-claims-against-livcor-over-alleged-anticompetitive-practices-2025-12-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部周二就针对 Blackstone 物业管理公司 LivCor 提出的诉讼达成和解，该诉讼指控相互竞争的房东通过软件平台共享租金定价信息，串谋提高租金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-proposes-resolve-claims-against-livcor-over-alleged-anticompetitive-practices-2025-12-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Dec 2025 21:14:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>列支敦士登法院在所有权案中裁定波兰 Cyfrowy Polsat 创始人败诉</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/boards-policy-regulation/liechtenstein-court-rules-against-founder-polands-cyfrowy-polsat-ownership-case-2025-12-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该公司周二表示，列支敦士登一家法院驳回了波兰亿万富翁 Zygmunt Solorz 的上诉，该上诉旨在推翻他将 Cyfrowy Polsat 媒体集团控股股东的所有权转让给其子女的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/boards-policy-regulation/liechtenstein-court-rules-against-founder-polands-cyfrowy-polsat-ownership-case-2025-12-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Dec 2025 12:15:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行 (HSBC) 的安·戈德比赫 (Ann Godbehere) 将退休，尼尔森 (Nelson) 的任命结束了主席搜寻工作</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbcs-ann-godbehere-retire-chair-search-ends-with-nelsons-appointment-2025-12-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股周二表示，负责寻找新主席的高级独立董事兼董事会成员 Ann Godbehere 将因“个人和生活方式原因”在该行 2026 年年度股东大会上辞职并退休。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbcs-ann-godbehere-retire-chair-search-ends-with-nelsons-appointment-2025-12-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Dec 2025 07:39:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ELFA 称 11 月份美国商业设备借款同比下降超过 4%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-business-equipment-borrowings-down-more-than-4-yy-november-elfa-says-2025-12-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[设备租赁和金融协会 (ELFA) 周一表示，与去年同期相比，11 月份美国公司为设备投资融资的借款减少了 4.4%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-business-equipment-borrowings-down-more-than-4-yy-november-elfa-says-2025-12-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Dec 2025 20:02:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华纳兄弟竞购战和并购市场火热，交易撮合者在假期里加班加点</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/litigation/warner-bros-bidding-war-red-hot-ma-market-has-dealmakers-working-through-2025-12-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普引发的贸易战导致第二季度的交易活动脱轨之后，今年对于交易撮合者来说是不平凡的一年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/litigation/warner-bros-bidding-war-red-hot-ma-market-has-dealmakers-working-through-2025-12-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Dec 2025 16:13:28 GMT</pubDate>
