    <item>
      <title>嘉能可收购荷兰燃料公司 FincoEnergies 多数股权</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/glencore-buys-majority-stake-dutch-fuel-company-fincoenergies-2025-12-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球大宗商品贸易商和矿业公司嘉能可 (Glencore) 周一表示，该公司已同意收购荷兰燃料供应商 FincoEnergies 的多数股权，收购金额未公开。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/glencore-buys-majority-stake-dutch-fuel-company-fincoenergies-2025-12-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Dec 2025 14:15:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储米兰表示，他可能会在任期结束后留下来，直到席位被填补为止</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/feds-miran-says-hell-likely-stay-after-term-ends-until-his-seat-is-filled-2025-12-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事史蒂芬·米兰周一表示，他可能会在任期届满后继续留在美联储理事会，直到唐纳德·特朗普总统提名的下一任美联储主席得到参议院确认。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/feds-miran-says-hell-likely-stay-after-term-ends-until-his-seat-is-filled-2025-12-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Dec 2025 14:11:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据彭博社报道，摩根大通正在探索为机构客户进行加密货币交易</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-exploring-crypto-trading-institutional-clients-bloomberg-news-reports-2025-12-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社周一报道，摩根大通正在考虑向其机构客户提供加密货币交易，这凸显了华尔街银行越来越多地参与数字资产领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-exploring-crypto-trading-institutional-clients-bloomberg-news-reports-2025-12-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Dec 2025 13:46:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲投资银行未能利用特朗普关税风暴</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/transactional/european-investment-banks-fail-capitalise-trump-tariff-turmoil-2025-12-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2025 年，华尔街银行在欧洲投资银行业的领先地位得到加强，尽管全球市场动荡且唐纳德·特朗普总统征收贸易关税，但客户仍保持忠诚度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/transactional/european-investment-banks-fail-capitalise-trump-tariff-turmoil-2025-12-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Dec 2025 13:41:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
